headline: AZZ (AZZ) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: AZZ (AZZ) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 7.75% and 0.84%, respectively, for the quarter ended November 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
